very deeply. you know.</i>

1164
00:59:55.801 --> 00:59:58.178
<i>I was very emotional.</i>

1165
00:59:58.261 --> 01:00:01.640
My dad. he had triggers.

1166
01:00:01.723 --> 01:00:05.519
<i>Charles dying
brought up past trauma.</i>

1167
01:00:05.602 --> 01:00:09.147
<i>[music warping]</i>

1168
01:00:11.775 --> 01:00:14.945
<i>Back then.
where he grew up in Memphis.</i>

1169
01:00:15.028 --> 01:00:16.988
{\an8}it was a rarity of having
a father in the house.

1170
01:00:18.406 --> 01:00:22.828
<i>Maurice's father was John White.</i>

1171
01:00:22.869 --> 01:00:27.499
<i>He was absent during most
of Maurice's childhood.</i>

1172
01:00:27.582 --> 01:00:33.046
<i>He owned a nightclub and was
part of that music scene.</i>

1173
01:00:33.088 --> 01:00:37.717
But he was also
this gangster figure.

1174
01:00:37.759 --> 01:00:39.594
<i>From what I understand.</i>

1175
01:00:39.678 --> 01:00:41.555
one day he went into
one of his establishments.

1176
01:00:41.638 --> 01:00:47.853
and somebody who was not
his same skin color shot him.

1177
01:00:49.813 --> 01:00:54.067
<i>He is killed before Maurice
is five years old.</i>

1178
01:00:56.945 --> 01:01:00.907
<i>When he talked
about his life as a child.</i>

1179
01:01:00.949 --> 01:01:03.160
{\an8}his knee would go... tschoo...

1180
01:01:03.243 --> 01:01:04.286
{\an8}like that.

1181
01:01:08.290 --> 01:01:13.003
<i>After Charles passed.
it was hard for him to accept.</i>

1182
01:01:13.086 --> 01:01:14.671
But the world doesn't care

1183
01:01:14.754 --> 01:01:17.424
who's gone and who is not gone.

1184
01:01:17.507 --> 01:01:20.927
It just keeps on rolling.

1185
01:01:21.011 --> 01:01:25.223
<i>Maurice learned almost
everything from Charles.</i>

1186
01:01:25.307 --> 01:01:28.018
Maurice was like. oh. my God.

1187
01:01:28.101 --> 01:01:29.311
Now what do I do?

1188
01:01:33.523 --> 01:01:36.943
[inhalation]

1189
01:01:36.985 --> 01:01:40.530
[exhalation]

1190
01:01:45.243 --> 01:01:49.831
<i>I started studying Egyptology.</i>

1191
01:01:49.915 --> 01:01:54.586
<i>I went into the pyramids
just to meditate.</i>

1192
01:01:54.669 --> 01:01:57.839
<i>It gave me new energy.
and I was able to evolve</i>

1193
01:01:57.923 --> 01:02:00.175
<i>into a different person.</i>

1194
01:02:00.258 --> 01:02:04.137
<i>It seemed like I was getting
help from the other side.</i>

1195
01:02:04.179 --> 01:02:06.306
<i>I was just fascinated
with the whole thing.</i>

1196
01:02:06.348 --> 01:02:09.434
<i>the artistic value of Egypt.</i>

1197
01:02:09.517 --> 01:02:12.562
<i>the contributions
that they made to society.</i>

1198
01:02:12.646 --> 01:02:14.981
{\an8}Look at how the pyramids
were built.

1199
01:02:15.023 --> 01:02:16.983
{\an8}with the science
and the technology.

1200
01:02:17.067 --> 01:02:21.154
<i>They are humanity at its finest.</i>

1201
01:02:21.238 --> 01:02:26.159
<i>Maurice begins learning
about Afrofuturism.</i>

1202
01:02:26.201 --> 01:02:30.121
<i>the idea that these ancient
civilizations are not</i>

1203
01:02:30.205 --> 01:02:33.792
just symbols of
Black people's past.

1204
01:02:33.875 --> 01:02:38.463
<i>they are also the future
and the infinite possibilities</i>

1205
01:02:38.505 --> 01:02:42.175
<i>that exist throughout
the universe.</i>

1206
01:02:42.217 --> 01:02:44.886
<i>the concept of space travel.</i>

1207
01:02:44.970 --> 01:02:49.849
<i>the existence of beings
on other planets.</i>

1208
01:02:49.933 --> 01:02:52.227
<i>The whole space concept. aliens.</i>

1209
01:02:52.310 --> 01:02:54.854
<i>just opened up a door for me.</i>

1210
01:02:54.896 --> 01:02:57.148
{\an8}My dad talked to me sometimes

1211
01:02:57.232 --> 01:02:59.234
{\an8}about astral projections.

1212
01:02:59.317 --> 01:03:01.152
{\an8}<i>He was like.
there was one time I felt</i>

1213
01:03:01.236 --> 01:03:03.238
{\an8}<i>like I was out of my body.</i>

1214
01:03:03.321 --> 01:03:04.781
{\an8}He would come back to the studio

1215
01:03:04.864 --> 01:03:09.035
{\an8}with these outrageous stories
of being

1216
01:03:09.077 --> 01:03:13.540
{\an8}picked up and taken in a
spaceship to another planet...

1217
01:03:13.623 --> 01:03:16.209
<i>[lively funk music]</i>

1218
01:03:16.251 --> 01:03:18.378
<i>And meeting with
extraterrestrials.</i>

1219
01:03:18.420 --> 01:03:20.880
And we didn't know
how to deal with this.

1220
01:03:20.964 --> 01:03:24.426
We just. you know. hey.
man. that sounds cool.

1221
01:03:28.221 --> 01:03:32.058
<i>I saw "Close Encounters
of the Third Kind."</i>

1222
01:03:32.100 --> 01:03:37.022
{\an8}<i>And I had a vision to write
the song "Fantasies."</i>

1223
01:03:37.063 --> 01:03:40.108
<i>And then all the words
started to come.</i>

1224
01:03:40.191 --> 01:03:42.736
â™ª Every man has a place â™ª

1225
01:03:42.819 --> 01:03:45.405
â™ª In his heart.
there's a space â™ª

1226
01:03:45.488 --> 01:03:51.369
â™ª And the world can't erase
this fantasy â™ª

1227
01:03:51.411 --> 01:03:53.747
â™ª Take a ride in the sky â™ª

1228
01:03:53.830 --> 01:03:56.416
â™ª On our ship. fantasize â™ª

1229
01:03:56.458 --> 01:04:01.921
â™ª All your dreams will
come true miles away â™ª

1230
01:04:02.005 --> 01:04:07.552
â™ª Our voices
will ring forever â™ª

1231
01:04:07.635 --> 01:04:12.849
â™ª Until the 12th of never â™ª

1232
01:04:12.932 --> 01:04:18.772
â™ª We all will live. love
forever â™ª

1233
01:04:18.855 --> 01:04:24.319
â™ª As one â™ª

1234
01:04:25.820 --> 01:04:26.863
<i>Everything that I had studied.</i>

1235
01:04:26.946 --> 01:04:29.949
<i>I was trying to share it
with the public.</i>

1236
01:04:30.033 --> 01:04:33.036
<i>so maybe it could help
to find themselves.</i>

1237
01:04:35.455 --> 01:04:37.791
<i>That's why.
on the album. "All 'N All."</i>

1238
01:04:37.874 --> 01:04:40.418
<i>it has a lot of symbols.</i>

1239
01:04:40.502 --> 01:04:44.631
<i>[ethereal music]</i>

1240
01:04:44.672 --> 01:04:46.841
<i>Through their album artwork.</i>

1241
01:04:46.925 --> 01:04:50.678
I think he was shining a light
on our history and our future

1242
01:04:50.762 --> 01:04:52.806
<i>and how it's related.</i>

1243
01:04:52.847 --> 01:04:54.808
He's inviting you
into this world.

1244
01:04:57.394 --> 01:04:59.437
<i>We had a lot of costumes
that were influenced</i>

1245
01:04:59.521 --> 01:05:02.982
<i>by Africa and space.</i>

1246
