The real statement
wasn't really made

1247
01:05:05.193 --> 01:05:08.488
{\an8}until Bill Whitten stepped in...

1248
01:05:08.571 --> 01:05:10.782
<i>very elaborate.</i>

1249
01:05:16.830 --> 01:05:18.289
<i>We changed our whole look.</i>

1250
01:05:21.000 --> 01:05:24.170
<i>We decided to expand the show.</i>

1251
01:05:24.254 --> 01:05:27.173
<i>We wanted to more or less
