1252
01:05:27.215 --> 01:05:29.426
<i>in order to get your attention.</i>

1253
01:05:32.387 --> 01:05:34.681
<i>[energetic music]</i>

1254
01:05:34.764 --> 01:05:37.016
<i>Maurice wasn't afraid
to spend the bread</i>

1255
01:05:37.058 --> 01:05:42.522
