on the A list of entertainment

1256
01:05:42.605 --> 01:05:44.816
to help Earth. Wind & Fire.

1257
01:05:44.899 --> 01:05:48.486
And the winner is
George Faison for "The Wiz."

1258
01:05:48.570 --> 01:05:52.323
[cheers and applause]

1259
01:05:52.407 --> 01:05:54.534
<i>Having choreographed "The Wiz."</i>

1260
01:05:54.576 --> 01:05:58.079
