1261
01:05:58.163 --> 01:06:00.582
<i>We had a black Dorothy.</i>

1262
01:06:00.665 --> 01:06:04.711
<i>That gave us another
kind of sense of pride.</i>

1263
01:06:04.794 --> 01:06:06.754
