1266
01:06:14.304 --> 01:06:15.430
<i>"All 'N All."</i>

1267
01:06:17.891 --> 01:06:20.894
<i>When it came on.
we were great musicians.</i>

1268
01:06:20.977 --> 01:06:24.564
<i>but we wasn't organized
