1269
01:06:24.606 --> 01:06:28.651
So could you tell me.
can all Black people dance?

1270
01:06:28.735 --> 01:06:30.570
No.

1271
01:06:30.653 --> 01:06:31.696
No.

1272
01:06:31.779 --> 01:06:33.656
And that's very true.

1273
01:06:33.740 --> 01:06:35.742
[laughter]

