1292
01:07:22.789 --> 01:07:25.124
<i>It's about evolution. you know?</i>

1293
01:07:25.208 --> 01:07:28.086
<i>I always had a lot of ideas.</i>

1294
01:07:28.169 --> 01:07:31.548
<i>We had started
to investigate. like. magic.</i>

1295
01:07:31.631 --> 01:07:33.883
The magic of Doug Henning.

1296
01:07:33.967 --> 01:07:37.303
[cheers and applause]

1297
01:07:37.345 --> 01:07:39.097
Doug Henning. at that time.
was the biggest

1298
01:07:39.180 --> 01:07:40.557
magician in the world.

1299
01:07:40.640 --> 01:07:41.724
<i>He had a show on NBC.</i>

1300
01:07:41.808 --> 01:07:45.144
<i>[energetic music]</i>

1301
01:07:45.228 --> 01:07:46.813
<i>So Maurice calls him.</i>

1302
01:07:46.854 --> 01:07:49.983
Everyone wondered. Maurice.
are you that crazy?

1303
01:07:50.024 --> 01:07:53.111
<i>It was so out of the box.</i>

1304
01:07:53.194 --> 01:07:56.281
Magic. music. dance.

1305
01:07:56.364 --> 01:07:59.158
