1308
01:08:04.455 --> 01:08:07.166
<i>We rehearsed every day
for six months.</i>

1309
01:08:07.250 --> 01:08:09.168
<i>It was really
the first production</i>

1310
01:08:09.210 --> 01:08:11.296
