{\an8}Reese would let me crawl in...
[laughs]

1327
01:08:56.174 --> 01:08:59.385
<i>To be
as unobtrusive as possible.</i>

1328
01:08:59.427 --> 01:09:06.225
â™ª â™ª

1329
